phrases: You can stop chopping wood now.
I am going to put it away.
I wish I could have her clean my room, too.
I think it should be done now.
It will be fifteen minutes in three more seconds.
Do you really need to be so precise?
What are you putting in there?
Do not do that in the main pot, please!
Why did you burn the rice?
We have never done this before!
We will do it ourselves, then.
Go keep an eye on the curry.
Do not act like you cannot hear me.
I am not letting you pretend you have forgotten about me.
You and Nakano-san are doing good, right?
You are lucky you have a partner for the folk dance.
How can I get a girlfriend?
Hey, are you listening to me?
I cannot wait for the rice to cook.
I am going to move all this test of courage stuff.
Were not you in charge of the campfire?
But I thought you might want some help.
You are here on this camping trip when you usually only camp out in front of textbooks.
I would like to support you as much as I can.
All right, Maeda, keep an eye on my group's dinner.
Do not go giving me orders!
And are not you going to hear me out?
The test of courage is optional.
Go invite a girl from class.
Just try not to freak out, because we are going to go all out.
The Quint es sen tial Quin tup let us
Come on, there has not been a single ghost.
What are the people in charge doing?
I was hoping the suspension bridge effect would do me a solid,
but this is not scaring her at all!
He is got a really scary look on his face!
Be the suspension bridge you want to see!?
I am so happy to see life in your dead eyes for once.
I am glad I have come back to life.
I was afraid you might not come.
Let us make sure we are not left with any regrets after school camp.
We are going to eat you!
Anyway, there is a dangerous cliff ahead.
There is a dangerous cliff ahead.
Be sure to follow the signs.
I sense doubt in the way you are scaring people.
You need to make a more elaborate entrance.
My classmates told me this forest is haunted.
Same thing with the campfire legend.
Who freaks out over such a cheap toy?
I thought this school camp would be more fun.
Instead, we had to share a room with him right off the bat.
Good thing nothing happened, I guess.
So that was not you, was it?
You finally got to see Futaro-kun.
You should have stayed a little longer.
Futaro is tutoring all five of us.
What do you think of Futaro, Ichika?
Is this even the right way?
School camp's supposed to be fun,
so why am I out here all alone?
It is the face from the photo!
Shit, she is going to kill me.
Sorry, it is just that I have seen you in a photo before.
I knew there were students from other schools at this camp,
but I never thought I would meet his relative.
So wait, does she think I am the guy in the photo?
Should I tell her the truth?
That the photo was actually of me?
But she might be able to blackmail me with it.
Oh, go straight down here and you will end up on a bigger path.
I got separated from my sister.
Could you help me find her?
Hurry up and get over here, Itsuki.
I am underage, but I want some booze.
I want to break the law.
Your sister may have headed back.
Five lengths below the Big Dipper is Polaris.
Now we know which way we are going.
You are way better than someone who loves showing off his grades.
Let me take a good look at your face.
You have a bruise on your forehead.
It will heal on its own.
One of my sisters always comes home injured.
Did you hear a voice or something?
Wait, my sister said this forest is haunted.
I have this good luck charm!
It will protect us from any kind of evil!
I would be too scared by myself!
Jeez, he is not very manly.
There is a path this way, too.
It is the edge of the forest, too.
I should be the one thanking you.
Maybe she really did head back.
Sorry, I do not think I can move.
Y-You know, we might be in for more scares here.
What am I saying to a guy I just met for the first time?
That is a really powerful good luck charm.
Hang onto it, and it will protect you for sure.
There are rumors that it will even grant your wishes.
Will you be here tomorrow too, Kintaro-kun?
My school's having a campfire tomorrow.
There is a legend about the folk dance that we do.
Any pair that is holding hands during the finale ends up together.
Some even say you will get together just by holding hands once.
The shyer students do it secretly, out of sight.
It is so overblown and childish.
I am surprised you were fine by yourself.
What do I think of Futaro-kun?
I think he is going through his awkward phase.
I mean, he is pretty unbalanced, do not you think?
Imagine if he grows up the way he is now.
How do you feel about Futaro?
Miku, I think we should trade spots for the dance.
You are worried, are not you?
These times are not going to last forever.
I wish school camp would last forever.
Do you have some good news?
This is a pain in the ass.
I could just dance with her in my disguise,
but I am already supposed to dance with Ichika.
I should tell Nino the truth.
Just who I wanted to see!
Oh, shoot, I just remembered I have work.
I am glad you are still here, though.
Wait, do they hate me more than I thought?
If you do not want it to get even worse,
I do not know what you are talking about.
I have to do something about this fast.
I am so glad you are here to help me.
You just want me to move these, right?
They were keeping them in here to avoid the snow.
The team is hard at work for the campfire tomorrow.
Are you actually a boy, Uesugi-san?
B-B-But it is always easier with more help.
I am just returning the favor for the test of courage.
I had to do all the scaring myself while you were gone.
It seems like I have been getting a lot of hate.
I need to regain their trust as soon as I can.
Let us get the next one.
Have I always been this weak?
Nanako-san, do you have a moment?
There is a key next to the she would door.
I thought you were someone else, Futaro-kun.
You were not assigned to this, were you?
It is not just Yotsuba, but also Ichika here.
This is a good chance for me to regain some respect.
I should have worn a jacket.
Please do not fail on me, my body!
Did you enjoy the test of courage?
Y-Yeah, it made my heart race.
As a member of the committee, I am most delighted.
Although my heart was also racing because I was not sure you could pull it off.
Why are you talking like that?
You do not go out of your way to talk to us outside of studying, huh?
Tell me what is on your mind.
So you do not want people to hate you.
Th-That is not really what I meant.
Your big sis here will help you practice, then.
I am not as good at this as Miku, but...
Are you even trying to hold it?
This is so heavy for me!
Hurry up and do your job.
I was so taken by you that I could not focus.
Okay, that was kind of weird.
Although even then, there is a trick to it.
Be as strong as Nino when you are talking to her.
And be nice when you are talking to Itsuki-chan.
And always use your own words.
Oh, you can be nice to me, too.
I am glad I got to talk to Ichika first.
She is not just the oldest sister for show.
She sees me and the sisters without prejudice.
Now, we are set for the campfire tomorrow.
You have heard from Miku, right?
Yeah, apparently we are supposed to be dancing tomorrow.
If I have to choose one or the other...
Like you said, it just kind of happened in the moment.
I cannot get over the legend thing, either.
And you can deal with Maeda if I am not there.
Besides, it would not be good for you if the others saw you dancing with me.
It is not what you think.
Sorry, can I put this down for a second?
Well, let us get it done and head back to the inn.
Huh, there is no more left.
Remember when this happened last time?
Is there a reason we are hiding?
Shoot, I just made it weird again.
Where is the key that was here?
Next Time on The Quintessential Quintuplets
That blond guy is your type, huh, Nino?
Blond hair dye is against school rules.
I bet he goes around not even working.
I will have to support him, will not I?
